description:
Storyline: American military veteran and former NATO operative Colonel Benjamin Ford (Robert De Niro) has fled to a cabin retreat somewhere in the Appalachian Mountains, to forget the painful memories of the Bosnian War he fought in. Former Serbian soldier Emil Kovac (John Travolta), intent on revenge against Ford for his actions during the war, poses as a European tourist visiting Tennessee and gets the opportunity to repair Ford's broken Land Rover. From there, the two men strike a friendly acquaintance. When Kovac reveals his true identity, after attacking Ford during a game hunting session, they become deadly enemies and what follows is a gory game of cat-and-mouse.


Cast: Robert De Niro
